{
  "info": {
    "name": "Finquanta AI Server API",
    "description": "Comprehensive financial management API for tracking income, expenses, and generating financial insights.\n\n## Features\n- JWT-based authentication system\n- Financial transaction management (CRUD operations)\n- Advanced filtering and search capabilities\n- Financial summary and analytics\n- Real-time WebSocket notifications\n- Comprehensive error handling\n- Rate limiting and security measures\n\n## Authentication\n\nThis API uses JWT (JSON Web Token) authentication. Include the token in the `Authorization` header:\n\n```\nAuthorization: Bearer <your-jwt-token>\n```\n\n## Getting Started\n\n1. **Register a new user account**\n2. **Login to receive access and refresh tokens**\n3. **Include the access token in API requests**\n4. **Refresh tokens when they expire**",
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_postman_id": "Finquanta-ai-server-api-v1",
    "_exporter_id": "Finquanta-ai-docs-generator"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{access_token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
